org.modelio.archimate.metamodel.relationships.other

Interface AndJunction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchimateAbstractElement, java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Concept, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Junction, MObject, ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RelationshipConnector

    public interface AndJunction
extends Junction
    AndJunction vnull

    The and junction is used to explicitly express that several elements together participate in the relationship (and junction)

    The junction should have more than one incoming relationships and one outgoing.

    It may be compared to the Join nodes in UMl activity and staate diagram.
